{
  "_comment": [
    "Bucket policy for the 'one bucket, many tenants' (Team / shared) layout.",
    "All tenants' bundles live in this bucket under per-tenant prefixes",
    "(`{tenant_id}/*`). The app role (skill-pool-server) is the only principal",
    "that can read or write objects; deny rules below stop everything else.",
    "Apply with:",
    "  aws s3api put-bucket-policy --bucket <BUCKET> --policy file://bucket-policy-shared.json",
    "Replace placeholders before applying:",
    "  <BUCKET_NAME>     — e.g. skill-pool-prod",
    "  <APP_ROLE_ARN>    — IAM role assumed by the skill-pool-server process",
    "                       (e.g. arn:aws:iam::123456789012:role/skill-pool-server)",
    "Tenant isolation between prefixes is enforced server-side by the app's",
    "`Storage::bundle_key(tenant_id, …)` (see server/src/storage.rs) — the",
    "bucket policy is the defence-in-depth layer that stops a leaked credential",
    "or a misconfigured client from reaching another tenant's objects."
  ],
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "DenyInsecureTransport",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::<BUCKET_NAME>",
        "arn:aws:s3:::<BUCKET_NAME>/*"
      ],
      "Condition": {
        "Bool": { "aws:SecureTransport": "false" }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowSkillPoolAppObjectAccess",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": { "AWS": "<APP_ROLE_ARN>" },
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:PutObject",
        "s3:DeleteObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::<BUCKET_NAME>/*"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowSkillPoolAppListBucket",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": { "AWS": "<APP_ROLE_ARN>" },
      "Action": "s3:ListBucket",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::<BUCKET_NAME>"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyEverythingElse",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "NotPrincipal": { "AWS": "<APP_ROLE_ARN>" },
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::<BUCKET_NAME>",
        "arn:aws:s3:::<BUCKET_NAME>/*"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
